"Being vulnerable is not a weakness. It's being human. It's allowing yourself to not have all the answers." 🌷
.
@dear.nesuto patisserie has the cutest sm0l cakes with a whirl of flavours in them. 😍 .
.
💗 : L'Amour ($10.80) - Vanilla souffle sponge with handcooked strawberry compote, fluffy citrus mousse and red velvet white chocolate spray ✨ .
.
💛  Le Petit Donut ($10.80) - Buttermilk dark chocolate sponge with Earl Grey infused Valrhona 40% Jivara chocolate mousse and tangy passionfruit curd. ✨ .
.
They are available to order from oddle.me. See @dear.nesuto to find out what cakes are available at the moment! 😉
